through the desert in heavy armor and wield heavy weapons near tirelessly against the Tribe's foes. Often accompanied by Tribal Shamans, they are the second most-elite group in the Tribe, surpassed only by the Devils.<br/><br/></span><span>\u00a0 \u00a0 The Devils are the personal guard of the Sheikh, comprised of warriors whose courage and devotion to the Tribe has been demonstrated again and again. To be appointed a Devil is the highest honor that can be bestowed upon a warrior, and oftentimes they are sent in the stead of the Sheikh, representing his interests on and off the battlefield. They too ride swift horses as the Jackals do, but are just as capable of fighting on foot, their gear a representation of their original caste.\u00a0<br/><br/><br/></span>(To be continued with Tribal customs, opinions on magic, etc.)</div></div></div></br></div>"}}